## Limitations

This report is based on available online sources and may not capture all recent developments in the luxury fashion industry's sustainability efforts. Additionally, the focus was on English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. The dynamic nature of the fashion industry means that strategies and targets may evolve, necessitating ongoing research to stay updated.

